section.def:
preparation
                (製劑) means a substance that is a mixture prepared
            by its manufacturer of 2 or more other substances;

substance
                (物質) means any natural or artificial substance
            whether in solid or liquid form or in the form of a gas or vapour;

tr.td:
In case
              of fire, use . . . (indicate in the space the precise type of fire-fighting equipment;
              if water increases the risk,
              add—“Never
              use
              water”)
